<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>My Calorie Balance Pro</title>
<meta name="description" content="Unlock premium features with My Calorie Balance Pro — advanced insights, unlimited history, priority support, and more." />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: #f4f6f4;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 820px;
    min-height: 560px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.10), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  /* Left panel */
  .left {
    width: 42%;
    background: #0c1a0f;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .left::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; left: -80px;
    width: 280px; height: 280px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2563eb;
    opacity: 0.10;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .left::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50px; right: -50px;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2563eb;
    opacity: 0.07;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .brand { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(37,99,235,0.18);
    border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 4px 13px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #60a5fa;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .badge-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #60a5fa; }

  .brand-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 30px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: #eef5f1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .brand-title em { font-style: italic; color: #60a5fa; }

  .brand-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(238,245,241,0.42);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .features {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .feat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 11px;
  }
  .feat-icon {
    width: 30px; height: 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(37,99,235,0.13);
    border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.18);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .feat-icon svg {
    width: 14px; height: 14px;
    stroke: #60a5fa;
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.6;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }
  .feat-text p { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(238,245,241,0.88); }
  .feat-text small { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(238,245,241,0.35); }

  /* Right panel */
  .right {
    flex: 1;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2.5rem 2.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Coming soon — right panel */
  .cs-rocket {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: #eff6ff;
    border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 26px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cs-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #0c1a0f;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .cs-sub {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: #6b7a6e;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .cs-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .cs-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    background: #f4f6f4;
    color: #3d5240;
    border: 1px solid #dde5de;
  }
  .cs-chip-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2563eb;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #aab5ab;
  }
  .divider::before, .divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: #eaeeea;
  }

  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6b7a6e;
  }
  .footer a {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .card { flex-direction: column; }
    .left { width: 100%; min-height: auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .features { display: none; }
    .right { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .cs-row { flex-direction: column; }
    .cs-btn { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

  <div class="left">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="badge"><div class="badge-dot"></div>Pro</div>
      <h1 class="brand-title">My Calorie<br /><em>Balance</em> Pro</h1>
      <p class="brand-sub">Cloud sync, coach access,<br />and insights that matter.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="12" height="10" rx="1.5" />
            <path d="M5 7h6M5 10h4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-text">
          <p>Cloud diary sync</p>
          <small>Access your diary from any device</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <circle cx="8" cy="5.5" r="2.5" />
            <path d="M3 13.5c0-2.76 2.24-5 5-5s5 2.24 5 5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-text">
          <p>Coach access</p>
          <small>Get feedback directly on your diary</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <polyline points="2,12 6,7 9,10 14,4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-text">
          <p>Advanced insights</p>
          <small>Trends, streaks & weekly progress</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M8 2v12M2 8h12" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-text">
          <p>Never lose your data</p>
          <small>Safely backed up to the cloud</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <div class="cs-rocket">🚀</div>

    <h2 class="cs-title">Pro is on its way</h2>
    <p class="cs-sub">
      We're building something worth waiting for — cloud sync, coach access, and deeper insights. Drop your email and you'll be the first to know when it launches.
    </p>

    <div class="cs-chips">
      <span class="cs-chip"><span class="cs-chip-dot"></span>Cloud sync</span>
      <span class="cs-chip"><span class="cs-chip-dot"></span>Coach access</span>
      <span class="cs-chip"><span class="cs-chip-dot"></span>Advanced insights</span>
      <span class="cs-chip"><span class="cs-chip-dot"></span>Data backup</span>
    </div>

    <div class="divider">or</div>
    <div class="footer">
      <a href="/">← Back to free app</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
